    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/383fa8c09184dc11710cd75b0fbd7fb7.avif?t=1721235207\" width=600 height=234 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game:</h2>Mini Pistons GT is a Top-Down 2D Arcade racing game inspired on GT Racing-like cars.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/ad05c06b9a3aef0e9b6dd604c2ab0399.poster.avif?t=1721235207\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/ad05c06b9a3aef0e9b6dd604c2ab0399.webm?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/ad05c06b9a3aef0e9b6dd604c2ab0399.mp4?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master your driving:</h2>Learn to drive and overtake to win races in mutiple circuits. You can compete in a single race or in a championship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/defacc71084ea598cc973405909ec3e2.poster.avif?t=1721235207\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/defacc71084ea598cc973405909ec3e2.webm?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/defacc71084ea598cc973405909ec3e2.mp4?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game includes:</h2>-8 total cars, 4 to unlock.<br>-10 circuits with different difficulty levels to drive and overtake.<br>-Quick Race mode.<br>-Championship mode. 3 different lengths to chose: 3, 5 or 10 races.<br>-You can save and continue your Championship progress later.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/98c51f4ec7acdd60703efd8330f57034.poster.avif?t=1721235207\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/98c51f4ec7acdd60703efd8330f57034.webm?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105780/extras/98c51f4ec7acdd60703efd8330f57034.mp4?t=1721235207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
